SUMMARY:BrainFest with Allen Institute
DTSTAMP:20260317T213913Z
DTSTART:20260321T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the third annual BrainFest\, a day of brainy fun fo
	r all ages at PacSci. Explore hands-on activities\, meet Allen Institute s
	cientists and collaborators\, learn about cutting-edge neuroscience resear
	ch\, and even touch a real brain! Whether you’re a budding young scientist
	\, a lifelong learner\, or simply fascinated by how the mind works\, Brain
	Fest 2026 promises a full day of discovery\, inspiration\, and wonder. Tic
	kets BrainFest is included with General Admission. A limited number of fre
	e general admission tickets will be given out on the day of the event on a
	 first-come first-serve basis. This event is a partnership of the Allen In
	stitute and Pacific Science Center.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events
	/#/details/brainfest-with-allen-institute/18033768/2026-03-21T00\n\nFrom S
